{
  "texts": [
    "The lessons were synchronously held online for 60 min for each group in the 4th -7th weeks of the implementation.",
    "During the synchronous online courses, the same teaching activities were organized for the students in the control and experimental groups.",
    "However, the application was different in terms of how the material was presented and used.",
    "In both groups, activities in online courses were organized by the same instructor (researcher).",
    "The population of this study consisted of 100 first-year medical students studying at a state university in Türkiye in the spring term of the 2021-2022 academic year."
  ]
}